                <div class="clearfix -medium-lpl -medium-up-xxxlpt -large-up-xlpl" role="main">
                    <div class="small-12 medium-10 large-8 columns">                        
                        <p class="t-intro -xlmb">
                        The old depot at 3rd and chicon,<br/>
